Decent, but small 18th floor pool and gym overlooking the City.	Did not utilize the fitness center or pool, but looked nice and clean.	Nice and clean gym on the top, typical hotel breakfast available downstairs.	The fitness center is very nice and very clean.	Wonderful views and the gym was very well equpped with the latest machines and free weights.	Used the pool and whirlpool once; the area was clean and all the equipment in the adjacent fitness center in working order.	The gym is huge and well equiped.	The kids loved the pool and I loved the fitness center with its complimentary headphones, oxygenated water and fresh fruit!